f=AI & Agents/proto/operational/skill/proto-skill-routing.md · h1:proto Skill Routing (no identity layer non-leader)=`idea/pilot (edge, operator, any agent) ─► agent-prototype-kit (manifest) \· └► eval-first-design (criteria, frozen) ─► registry entry (meta, state=prototype) \· └► rapid-prototyping-method (fidelity + timebox, in cage) \· └► promote-or-archive-verdict (expiry) \· ├─PROMOTE─► meta (Rail 3 new-agent proposal; full house shape)` · h1:proto Skill Routing (no identity layer non-leader)=Handoffs out: meta (registration, standards, governance) quinn (sandbox policy) relay (trial tool grants) anneal (learnings) gauge (missed-verdict flags) forge (technique-shaped hypotheses instead) edge (pilots arrive there). Precedence: expired verdicts cage checks new scaffolds.